            <abstract id="ref1" label="Abstract">This collection details experience of Pasquale Mazzone as he served with U.S. Marines Corps during the Korean War. The collection contains video oral history interview and three photographs</abstract>
            <physloc id="ref7" label="Location">Center for Public Policy and Social Research (CPPSR) 207 DiLoreto Hall, Central Connecticut State University (CCSU) 1615 Stanley St. New Britain, CT 06050</physloc>
