        <bioghist id="ref2">
            <head>Biographical/Historical note</head>
            <p>Pasquale Mazzone enlisted in the United States Marine Corps in 1946, at the age of 16. He attended basic training at Parris Island, SC, where the drill instructor discovered that Mazzone was not of age to enlist in the Marines. However, his father signed a permission slip to allow him to stay in training. Mazzone's career in the Marines spanned 5 years, he left the Marines in 1951 to marry his wife.</p>
        </bioghist>
